flowchart
  A[Start<br>Scan for batches in total_verified state] --> B{All currency<br>batches verified for that batch?}
  B -- No --> C[Wait for<br>other batches]
  B -- Yes --> D[Generate Intact<br>journal entries]

  D --> E{Journal totals<br>match<br>batch totals?}
  E -- No --> F[Do not upload<br>and alert fr-tech]
  E -- Yes --> G[Upload to Intact<br>via CSV or API]

  G --> H[Archive journal<br>output]
  F --> H
  H --> I[End]
